    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: 1. Core Content: Same data, different presentation. 2. Callouts: Used for the quote and main CTA to make them stand out, just like in Notion. Implemented with custom CSS. 3. Toggles: The FAQ and Academic Info sections now use a clean, Notion-style toggle design with a rotating triangle icon, created with CSS and a <span>, enhancing the document feel. 4. Charts/Tabs: These are treated as "embedded blocks" within the Notion page, preserving interactivity within the clean new structure. -->
